com.leantegra.wibeat.sdk.monitoring.listeners

Interface ScanServiceConsumer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BackgroundScanServiceConsumer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvertisingNotificationManager

    public interface ScanServiceConsumer
    The interface is used in ScanServiceManager and provides callbacks indicating whether the service connection state has changed.

    Note: Ranging and monitoring of WiBeats is available after onBind() callback.
    Since:
    1.4.0
    See Also:
    ScanServiceManager
